import React from 'react'

import {Nav} from 'react-bootstrap'

function Header(){
    <Nav
    activeKey="/home"
    onSelect={(selectedKey) => alert(`selected ${selectedKey}`)}
    >
    <Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Link href="/">Start</Nav.Link>
    </Nav.Item>
    <Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Link eventKey="Main">Main</Nav.Link>
    </Nav.Item>
    </Nav>
}

export default Header
